PrecisEnactment of the PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1995, NO. 6 - which prohibits the staking of mineral claims on specific lands in the Klondike Valley in the Yukon Territory which are required for the settlement of land claims made by the Dawson First Nation.
